    <div class="narrative">
      <p>In the heart of the Citadel, behind a door that few archivists know about, lies the Infinite Library. Its corridors stretch so far that no one has ever seen the end. The shelves groan under the weight of archives so vast that no ordinary scroll could contain them - immense datasets, complex predictive models, experiment grimoires spanning hundreds of thousands of pages.</p>
