      <p>"You've learned to version code. That's good. But code is only part of the story. Data, models, experiments - that's <strong>the real treasure</strong> of the Library. And these treasures are so large, so complex, that they require special tools. Follow me, I'll teach you <strong>the art of versioning the infinite</strong>."</p>
